name: Dungeon Flipper
overview: This great pinball machine offers pinball fun for 1 to 4 players. Conquer the 2 game levels and put your skills to the test. Sure, it's something of a classic, but it's still one of the most addictive pinball machines we've ever played. You have to put your pinball skills to the test in 2 game levels with different game images. Pinball kings can of course immortalize themselves by name. 1-4 players can compete against each other.
